2.content: Hello, how can I assist you with your health or wellness today?

4.content: Hello, I'm your friendly health assistant. I'm here to help you with any questions or concerns you may have about your health and wellness. I have access to your medical history and other relevant information, so feel free to ask me anything. Whether it's about your medications, test results, or just general advice on how to stay healthy, I'm here to help.
